<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
  <style>
    button {
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: black;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-right: 10px;
    }

    input {
      padding: 10px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    input {
      margin-left: auto;
    }

    /* Styling specific to the Mercury Slideshow Gallery page */
    h1 {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .gallery {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .image-container {
      margin: 10px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .image-container img {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }

    .image-container img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.1);
    }

    /* Additional styling for the Mercury page */
    .uranus-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .uranus-image {
      width: 400px;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .uranus-facts {
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .close {
      opacity: 0;
      position: absolute;
      top: 10px;
      right: 10px;
      font-size: 30px;
      color: #fff;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
  </style>
  <title>Uranus</title>
</head>

<body>
  <div id="wrapper">
  <header>
    <h1>Galactic Explorer</h1>
    <nav>
      <button onclick="goBack()">Back</button>
    </nav>
  </header>
  <main>
    <h1>Uranus</h1>
    <div class="gallery" onclick="openModal()">
      <div class="image-container">
        <img src="/img/planetImg/uranus1.jpg" alt="Uranus 1">
      </div>
      <div class="image-container">
        <img src="/img/planetImg/uranus2.jpg" alt="Uranus 2">
      </div>
      <div class="image-container">
        <img src="/img/planetImg/uranus3.jpg" alt="Uranus 3">
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- The Modal -->
    <div id="myModal" class="modal">
        <img style="height: 100vh; width: 100vh;" class="modal-content" id="modalImage" />
        <span style="cursor: pointer" id="close" onclick="closeModal()">&times;</span>
      </div>

    <div class="uranus-facts">
      <h3>Facts About Uranus</h3>
      <p>
        Uranus, the seventh planet in our solar system, is a captivating ice giant known for its distinct blue-green color, attributed to methane in its atmosphere. Unlike most planets, Uranus rotates uniquely on its side, resulting in pronounced seasonal changes. Composed mainly of water, ammonia, and methane, Uranus lacks a solid surface. It boasts a system of faint rings and a collection of moons, including notable ones like Titania and Oberon. Discovered by Sir William Herschel in 1781, Uranus continues to intrigue scientists, offering valuable insights into the diverse celestial bodies within our cosmic vicinity.</p>
      <!-- Add more facts as needed -->
    </div>

    <div style="padding-bottom: 1rem;">
      <h4>Credits:</h4>
      <p>These facts are sourced from [NASA]. Visit their website for more information: <a href="https://www.nasa.gov/" target="_blank">[https://www.nasa.gov/]</a></p>
    </div>

  </main>
</div>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2023 Galactic Explorer</p>
  </footer>

 <script>document.getElementById('myModal').style.display = 'none';</script>
  <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
